    "name": "Approach3-AdaptiveEpochMonitoring-MultiMetric-100K-iter5-fix2-comp",
    "description": "APPROACH 3 iter5-fix2-comp: COMPRESSED FULL-CYCLE DEMO\n\nDemonstrates complete MINT \u2192 HALT \u2192 RESTORE lifecycle in 46 epochs over 72h.\nAll thresholds at GENIUS/MiCA regulatory values. Only contract amounts and\nmaturity dates tuned for compressed demonstration.\n\nREGULATORY THRESHOLDS (unchanged from iter5-fix2):\n  BACKING_THRESHOLD  = 1.00  (100% MtM-adjusted \u2014 GENIUS/MiCA requirement)\n  LIQUIDITY_THRESHOLD= 0.20  (20% cash/supply \u2014 MiCA Art.45)\n  QUALITY_THRESHOLD  = 70    (HQLA weighted quality score)\n  EW_HALT_SIGNALS    = 4     (all 4 early-warning signals trigger halt)\n\nPORTFOLIO: $101,000 reserves vs $100,000 token supply (1% over-collateral)\n  cash-reserve-001:    $12,000  (HQLA L1, perpetual)\n  operating-cash-001:  $11,000  (HQLA L1, perpetual)\n  tbill-4wk-001:       $10,000  matures 2026-03-05 = h=48 \u2190 RESTORE TRIGGER\n  tbill-13wk-001:      $32,000  (HQLA L1, matures 2026-04-21)\n  tbill-26wk-001:      $26,000  (HQLA L1, matures 2026-06-15)\n  commpaper-90d-001:    $6,000  (HQLA L2A, matures 2026-04-15)\n  defi-yield-001:       $4,000  (HQLA L2B, matures 2026-06-01)\n\nCOMPRESSED RUN PARAMETERS:\n  SIM_END_HOURS=72  MAX_EPOCHS=60\n  NORMAL=6h  WATCH=3h  ELEVATED=2h  CRITICAL=1h\n\nLIFECYCLE (dry-run validated):\n  Ep1  h=0:  MINT ALLOWED \u2705  \u2014 NORMAL cadence (6h)\n  Ep2  h=6:  Peg 0.10% \u2192 WATCH (3h)\n  Ep4  h=12: Peg 0.30% \u2192 ELEVATED (2h)\n  Ep7  h=18: EW 1/4 fires (curve imbalance 17%)\n  Ep9  h=22: EW 2/4 \u2014 CRITICAL (1h)\n  Ep10 h=23: EW 3/4\n  Ep11 h=24: \u2605 MINT HALTED \ud83d\uded1 \u2014 EW=4/4 fires simultaneously\n  Ep22 h=35: Liquidity also drops below 20% (dual halt condition)\n  Ep31 h=44: EW drops to 3/4 (curve imbalance clears first)\n  Ep32 h=45: EW drops to 0/4 (all 4 signals clear)\n  Ep35 h=48: \u2605 4wk T-bill MATURES \u2192 +$10,000 cash \u2192 Liq 17.5%\u219228.1%\n             \u2605 MINT RESTORED \u2705 (backing 101%, liq 28%, EW 0/4)\n  Ep40 h=53: DE-ESC CRITICAL\u2192ELEVATED (peg<1.0%, 2 good epochs)\n  Ep44 h=61: DE-ESC ELEVATED\u2192WATCH\n  Ep46 h=67: DE-ESC WATCH\u2192NORMAL\n  h=73:      FINAL SUMMARY\n\nONLY REQUIRES: actus-server on localhost:8083\nrisksrv3 NOT NEEDED \u2014 all 11 models computed in JS",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
